title: #90 - Celebrity ASMR & Elon Musk Suspended From Twitter
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan and Hila continue their quest to determine life's most important questions via the most scientific method known to man: twitter polls. We also speak to Gibi ASMR and finally clear up some misconceptions about what ASMR is all about, watch a video about a man who can't stop burping, and talk about Elon Musk coming out of the weeb closet.
